      "comment": "GRUBBER KICK (4) has a strong record here with seven wins and a minor from 14 starts. Scored by one length last time (19.11) in a Grade 5 over 350m at Q Straight. Looks a key chance on best form. PERKY PENNY (1) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (28.16) last time out at Casino. Form at this distance is sound. The form out of last race has been strong. Will give a great sight again. PSIONIC PROWESS (6) held her own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only 0.8 lengths (19.98) behind Free Settler at Capalaba. Expected to be in this for a long way. FROM A DISTANCE (2) generally performs well here at this distance.",
